text: Lena Maryana Mukti (born 22 December 1962) is an Indonesian politician who is a member of the People's Representative Council. ==Career== Lena Maryana Mukti was born on 22 December 1962 in Jakarta, the second child of ten. She was elected into the People's Representative Council in 2004 following the 2004 Indonesian legislative election. once more ran in the 2014 Indonesian legislative election, still as a PPP candidate. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the People's Representative Council, 2004 Category:Members of the People's Representative Council, 2014 Category:Women members of the People's Representative Council Category:20th- century women politicians Category:21st-century women politicians Category:Politicians from Jakarta
